values: Hello. I have not updated this in i don't know how long! Well, any ways my life is just really fucked up! If I seem different it is because I am getting back into my hole again. I am trying not to but it never gets better just worst. Let's start off with what the main problem is. My SISTER!!!!!!!!!!! I don't know if she realizes this but it is not just her life she is screwing up, her actions affect everyone around her. Over the summer she had a miscarriage and I guess that is what started it all. As you all know I felt really guilty for all of that. Then she gets this life changing DREAM!!!! What the hell am I doing. None of you all give a flying fuck about me. I can't believe how fucking naive I am.
http://unlovablegirl.livejournal.com/3958.html

HELLO TO ANYONE WHO READS THIS. I HAVE NOT UPDATED MY JOURNAL IN AWHILE AND THOUGHT THAT I MIGHT WRITE A LITTLE SINCE I HAVE NOTHING ELSE TO DO. THURSDAY IS MY REGISTRATION FOR SCHOOL. I AM EXCITED. I AM READY FOR SCHOOL TO START! I GET SO BORED DURING THE SUMMER! WELL, I AM STARTING TO GET PISSED ABOUT THAT NIGHT. EVERY YEAR SINCE I HAVE BEEN IN HIGH SCHOOL MY FRIENDS AND I HAVE DONE SOMETHING ON REGISTRATION NIGHT. WELL THIS YEAR IT HAS BEEN SOOOOO HECTIC (COULD BE SPELLED WRONG) AND IT IS MAKING ME ANGRY. NOBODY WILL SAY WHAT THEY WANT TO DO. WE FINALLY HAVE A PLAN AND IF IT CHANGES I AINT GOING! I AM REALLY EXCITED. I HAVE A JOB INTERVIEW TOMORROW! I HOPE I GET THIS BECAUSE IF I DON'T I WILL HAVE TO WORK AT SUBWAY AND THEY AREN'T FLEXIBLE WITH THE HOURS OF MY SCHEDULE. I NEED A JOB THOUGH REALLY BAD! I HOPE I GET THIS. WELL, I GOT BORED TODAY AND WAS LOOKING UP SOME INFORMATION ON WESTERN KENTUCKY. THAT IS THE COLLEGE I WISH TO GO TO. THEY HAVE CHANGED THE RULES TO NOW FRESHMAN AND SOPHOMORES MUST LIVE ON CAMPUS. BUT THAT IS FINE. I WAS THINKING THE WRONG THING ALL ALONG. I AM JUST GOING TO LIVE IN AN APARTMENT ON CAMPUS. I THOUGHT LIVING ON CAMPUS MEANT LIVING IN A DORM. DORKY ME!! WELL, I HAVE BEEN CHECKING OUT SOME APARTMENT PLACES AND THEY ARE KIND OF EXPENSIVE BUT I WOULD RATHER LIVE IN AN APARTMENT THAN A DORM BECAUSE I JUST DON'T LIKE THE IDEA OF A DORM. I WILL PROBABLY END UP LIVING IN A DORM ALL OF MY YEARS THROUGH COLLEGE. WELL, I AM RUNNING OUT OF THINGS TO SAY. BYE!
http://unlovablegirl.livejournal.com/3666.html

Today was really fun. I went over to Amanda's house to go swimming. It was a blast. I was a little sad that Sarah had to leave so early. Well, we talked about a lot of things but mostly just swam. We played a lot of water volleyball. (Sandra, me and you make a good team!) I don't know what else to say. My life has been boring lately. I am soooooooo ready for school to start back up. This year is junior ring dance. I am going to go but I just wish I had a date. Well, to be frank I wish I had a boyfriend! (Damn you Sandra) Just Joking. I am really happy for you. Well, I was just writing because i haven't wrote in awhile. I hope Dustin is having fun. I  just hope that those e-mails were sent after he left. Okay well, bye.
http://unlovablegirl.livejournal.com/3439.html

I am sure those of you who know me know heard that my sister was pregnant. Well, I got all excited and went out and bought her a baby outfit and everything and now I feel really guilty. She lost the baby. I feel responsible because I knew something didn't feel right. The day that it happened I tried getting a hold of her early in the day because I woke up with this feeling that something was wrong with her or something bad was going to happen to her. I know how crazy this sounds considering ..... well that you aren't me. I get "feelings" a lot and they are almost always correct. I knew something was wrong and I didn't tell her or anybody I tried dealing with it on my own and I was right. I just feel so fucking guilty. I had to excited and buy her things and talk to her about the baby and when something didn't feel right I kept it to myself and when people said things I told them to be positive and that everything would be fine. But deep inside I knew it wouldn't and I didn't say shit. Now I'm in a situation where I feel like shit but can't show it because my sister is the one who needs the support. Well, I hope all is well in anyone who reads this life. If not I think I am living through enough bad for all of you. Well, I gotta run.

Hey. I am really bored. Let me just say that my friends suck! I don't think you all have been on the internet in forever. if you have you have had nothing to talk about. Especially you Dustin. You haven't updated your journal since last month. You all don't really suck. (Well, at least that I know of.) Well, like I said I am bored. Just thought I would write something.

Alright I know it is a part of everyday life. My subject is a lie. I love to clean and organize. But that is me. I do it for me. I don't do it to please anyone else. My dad makes me clean and organize the house. I know it may not sound like a big deal but it would be if you only knew how it made me feel. I would do it if he wouldn't ask me to do it all the time. When he asks me it makes me feel like I am the size of a fly. It just really hurts. I know it needs to be done he knows it needs to be done and God knows I am the only fucking person in the house that will do it. It's just that I don't feel like dong it when someone asks me to do it. I feel like his fucking slave! What I don't understand is if he wants it done so bad why can't he do it for himself. I know why. It makes the mother fucker feel more superior to me. I hate living in this fucking house. I want to graduate to get the hell out. Better yet I want to turn 18 so I can move into my grandma's house.
http://unlovablegirl.livejournal.com/1992.html

I was just lying in my bed a few minutes ago thinking about what I was going to do tomorrow. I thought since my grandma is getting older and she is exhausted that I would watch my nephew so she could have a break. I called my sister to ask and she was stand offish of the idea. Now, I probably should not take offense but I did. Ever since he was a few months old she does no like me watching him. I just found out why. The last time I watched him he fell and got a bump on his head. I guess that is my fault. Chad was seven months old at the time and was just learning to walk. She does not want that happening again. She said she would have to ask Chad's dad and see what he thought. But now that I'm thinking, Chad gets hurt constantly over at my grandma's. Babies get hurt. It is what they do! I don't know it just really got to me. I mean I base my whole life on my niece and nephew and know people are questioning how good I am with kids. That is what I want to do with my life for God sake! I want to work with children but I guess I am not as good as I thought I was with them.
http://unlovablegirl.livejournal.com/1743.html

Incase you couldn't tell by the subject my mom and I are fighting. One of my friends is suppose to be getting her liscence next week. Well, Lindsay asked me to ask my mom if she could drive me to this church thing on the 9th if she had her liscence by then. Well, I knew that one was going to be a no. However, what's the harm in asking. Lindsay also wanted for me to ask my mom if she could drive me to school on the first day. Guess what? My mom said no! I am very angry with her. My father was saying no also but I won him over. My sister was in a car with her boyfriend less than two days after he got his liscence and he is nearly six months younger than her. She said that she didn't want me dying in a car with a 16 year old driving. What the fuck is that? She also told me that she allowed me to do more than my two of my sibilings because she trusts me more! BULLSHIT!!!!!!! My parents shelter me so much that I don't know how I know what drving is! It is not only that but my mom is such a manipulater. (That could be spelt wrong!) Well, I'm on the phone with Sandra and I have to get off.
http://unlovablegirl.livejournal.com/1327.html

Okay. i hate that my family is so different. Nobody wants to do anything. They all want to live their own lives and if they bump into a family member that's fine. I am sick of it! I love when my immediate family gets together but nobody wants to do it anymore. Well, actually it's not everyone. But most of the people don't want anything to do with it. I love my grandma. She is my most favorite person but lately I can't stand to be around her. Well, tears are starting to fall so i have to go. Hope everyone is okay.

Okay here is what has been going on. I have been trying to lose weight. Well, I have been trying for years now and I had lost some weight. However nobody noticed. That didn't really bother me though because I noticed. Well, this summer I was so determined and I just haven't done it. Well, I really want to lose twenty pounds this summer. Anyways, I have been having these thoughts that maybe if I made myself throw up that it would it help. I mean I know it would it's just that I don't think it is the right thing to do. If you could anybody who reads this just please tell me what you think.
People that know me I am NOT looking for compliments.
http://unlovablegirl.livejournal.com/990.html

Hey. Well, this is one of the things I have been thinking about lately. GUYS HAVE IT SOOOOOOOOOO EASY!!!!!!!!!!! I am not talking about life in general but in the subject of relationships. Guys are the ones that can tell the person that they like them. They seem so unafraid. I, as a girl, can't do that. I am risking to many things. One they could say no and I would be rejected, two they could start a rumor about me, or three I could come become known as a slut. It is not fair. I really like this guy and I can't do anything about it. He also has a girlfriend (that all the guys think is hot which means I have no shot with him.) which makes me seem like an even bigger slut! That's my problem. I fall for guys that are taken. Example, Seth. He had a girlfriend and was not interested in me at all. I mean can you blame him. But now I don't like Seth like that I like this other guy who is also taken. I don't know it is just really getting to me. I mean Dustin (for example) could have just walked up to Candice and said "Candice I like you." (Sorry Dustin just wanted to throw some humor in there. I know you don't like Candice) However I can't walk up and say "Andy I like you." He would laugh in my face. Not to mention I would lose a friend. I am just totally lost now. I want to write another entry so I am going to stop this one now.
http://unlovablegirl.livejournal.com/722.html

Okay, this is my first journal. I just want to explain what has been going on with me. Sandra and Dustin I'm sorry. I don't want you to think that I have been mad at you lately. I have been going through a lot lately and pushed a lot of people away. I came out with a lot this year (I think you both know what I'm talking about) but things have changed. I don't want to dwell on that anymore. I didn't like how I was being seen. I told people (parents) that I was better ( I was lying) so I wouldn't have to deal with it anymore. Dustin this is the first part of me you met.  That's not who I am and I didn't know if you would accept the real me. Sanadra we became really close because of this and I didn't want to ruin anything because of this new information. I guess I did anyways. So there, now you know what has been up with me. I am sorry. I just don't want to be the depressed girl anymore. Please don't be mad. 
I love ya,
Brittany
P.S. Dustin happy late birthday!!!
